LGTM

More details needed here.  "Manager" is a somewhat ephemeral concept in redfish, so it's not super clear why a manager would ever be anything but "embedded".  In the DC-SCM case, the manager (ie bmc) is embedded into the DC-scm module, which is represented under chassis, and should be connected through "ManagerForChassis" and "ContainedBy"
PTAL
And ServiceLabel works like it did before?
I guess you tested this helper function in pervious commits

yeah, just tested this out and works fine with ServiceLabel.

My setup was missing the ServiceLabel for the Manager. Just added it and works fine like before.
